'''Creative Commons Noncommercial''' often shortened to '''NC''' is clause in the [[Creative Commons]] license that restricts sharing and use to [[Non-commercial licenses vs open licenses|Noncommercial]] use.

Content licensed with this clause is not usable on [[Appropedia]]. See [[Non-commercial licenses vs open licenses]] for discussion why.

For details on why the Appropedia Foundation chose the [[CC-BY-SA]] license, which allows commercial use, and the problems with Non-Commercial licenses, see ''[[Non-commercial licenses vs open licenses]]''.

